Package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.schemagen.json.schema

Interface IDefineableJsonSchema

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IJsonSchema
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDefineableJsonSchema, AbstractDefinitionJsonSchema, AssemblyDefinitionJsonSchema, DataTypeJsonSchema, DataTypeRestrictionDefinitionJsonSchema, FieldDefinitionJsonSchema, FlagDefinitionJsonSchema
    public interface IDefineableJsonSchema
extends IJsonSchema
    A type of IJsonSchema that can represent a schema that is a global definition.

    A schema of this type will be a global definition if IJsonSchema.isInline(JsonGenerationState) is false.
